### Signup (local)
POST http://localhost:3003/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"student@example.com",
  "password":"password123",
  "displayName":"Student"
}

###

### Login (local)
POST http://localhost:3003/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"student@example.com",
  "password":"password123"
}

###

### Google OAuth (open in browser)
GET http://localhost:3003/auth/google

###

### Get all games
GET http://localhost:3003/games

###

### Create a game (requires logged-in session)
POST http://localhost:3003/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Game",
  "platform": "PC",
  "genre": "Indie",
  "rating": "E",
  "releaseDate": "2025-01-01",
  "developer": "Test Studio",
  "coverArt": "https://example.com/test.jpg"
}

###

### Update game (requires login)
PUT http://localhost:3003/games/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": "T"
}

###

### Delete game (requires login)
DELETE http://localhost:3003/games/{id}
